  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in tomato paste and cumin powder, cook for another minute.",
    "Fold in kidney beans, dates, orange slices, and their juice. Add salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Pour in enough water or vegetable broth to cover the ingredients.",
    "Simmer gently on low heat for about 15 minutes until the liquid is reduced slightly.",
    "Stir in lemon juice before serving."
